of Abnormal Psychology.]

19:26.330 --> 19:28.594
- You want a writing partner?

19:28.630 --> 19:30.621
- [Could we meet?]

19:52.020 --> 19:53.749
- Hello?

19:55.890 --> 19:58.222
Dr. Carruthers?

19:58.260 --> 20:01.752
- Ms. Lounds, come on in.

20:06.770 --> 20:08.863
Now, you wrote
in your Tattler archive

20:08.900 --> 20:11.004
that the Chesapeake Ripper
once removed a man's tongue

