a Colombian necktie.

20:18.910 --> 20:20.514
What do you think?

20:22.520 --> 20:23.919
Ee...

20:33.030 --> 20:36.693
- Dr. Paul Carruthers wrote
an article for the Journal
of Criminal Psychology

20:36.730 --> 20:38.789
in which he described Dr. Gideon
as being

20:38.830 --> 20:41.936
a pathological narcissist who
suffers from psychotic episodes.

20:41.970 --> 20:45.599
- Let's hope he got some
satisfaction from being
proved right.

20:45.640 --> 20:48.973
- I think this is
about more than just
getting the Chesapeake

20:49.010 --> 20:50.978
Ripper's attention.
- Gideon's mind was

20:51.010 --> 20:53.001
dissected by psychiatrists

20:53.050 --> 20:57.384
and, as a surgeon, he is
applying his own skill set.

20:57.420 --> 21:01.959
He gave you something better
to do with your tongue
than wag it.

21:01.990 --> 21:04.356
- No, that's not how he died.

21:04.390 --> 21:07.029
Drained him
till his heart stopped.

21:07.060 --> 21:09.324
- Got a little on his collar.
Other than that,

21:09.360 --> 21:11.920
didn't spill a drop.
- That's because it's all

21:11.970 --> 21:14.268
in here. Four-and-a-half liters
all packed in ice.

21:17.370 --> 21:19.361
"Please deliver
to the Red Cross."

21:19.410 --> 21:22.402
- (Bev): That's considerate.
- He's peacocking
for the Ripper.

21:22.440 --> 21:25.603
- This is like flowers and
chocolate before a first date.

21:41.100 --> 21:43.523
- How is this news already?

21:43.570 --> 21:47.461
- Somebody from the Baltimore PD
must've taken a picture with
their phone and sold it

21:47.500 --> 21:49.764
to TattleCrime.
- The photo was taken

21:49.800 --> 21:52.598
before the blood was put on ice.
Dr. Gideon was still here.

21:52.640 --> 21:56.974
- He has Freddie Lounds.

21:57.010 --> 22:00.070
- You might be working out
the emergency exits,

22:00.110 --> 22:02.510
or at_ least
